{"tid":1633961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐港解放軍 高調警告示威者","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:57:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08dcf9ce89adb38c31e010e8f6841d32202be927","tid":1633961,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/img.ltn.com.tw/2019/new/oct/7/images/bigPic/600_161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2019%2Fnew%2Foct%2F7%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F600_161.jpg&h=ec332096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n香港「反惡法港人合理非」大遊行六日下午途經九龍塘中國人民解放軍駐港部隊九龍東軍營時，示威者以鐳射筆照射軍營頂樓上的軍人，解放軍首度舉出寫有「你正在違反法例，可能被檢控」的黃旗警告，並以廣東話回應：「後果自負！」此前，針對解放軍的抗議行動多出現在港島、駐港部隊總部大樓，但多以鐳射筆照射總部大樓的監視攝影機，六日是首度出現解放軍現身警告。 （路透）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/paper/1323076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1323076&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4rTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=b0fef1af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/paper/1323076</a><br />\n<br />\n個黃旗係咪問差佬借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}